<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>خدمات منزل | بهترین سرویس‌های نظافت و تعمیرات</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Tahoma', sans-serif;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
            background-color: #f4f8fb;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(34, 193, 195, 0.7), rgba(253, 187, 45, 0.7)), url('https://source.unsplash.com/1600x900/?home,cleaning');
            background-size: cover;
            height: 70vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 30px 30px;
        }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                max-width: 600px;
            }

        .auth-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .btn-login, .btn-signup {
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-login {
            border: 2px solid white;
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
        }

            .btn-login:hover {
                background: white;
                color: #22c1c3;
            }

        .btn-signup {
            background: #fd7e14;
            color: white;
        }

            .btn-signup:hover {
                background: #e76f00;
            }

        .search-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .search-container input {
                border-radius: 25px;
                padding: 14px;
                width: 100%;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

        .btn-search {
            background-color: #28a745;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

            .btn-search:hover {
                background-color: #218838;
            }

        .card {
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: 0.3s;
            background: #fff;
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            }

        footer {
            background: #22c1c3;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark" style="background: #fd7e14;">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">خدمات منزل</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#services">خدمات</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#about">درباره ما</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">تماس با ما</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="auth-buttons ms-3">
                    <button class="btn-login">ورود</button>
                    <button class="btn-signup">ثبت نام</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>بهترین خدمات منزل را از ما بخواهید</h1>
        <p>ارائه خدمات نظافت، تعمیرات و جابجایی با بالاترین کیفیت و مناسب‌ترین قیمت</p>
    </header>

    <div class="search-container">
        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="جستجو کنید...">
        <button class="btn btn-search">🔍 جستجو</button>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; ۲۰۲۵ تمامی حقوق محفوظ است.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
